        <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-10">
          Schedule a personalized demo to see how BharatDCIM can transform
          your data center billing operations.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-light text-lg px-8 py-4">Request Demo</a>
          <a href="/calculator" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 text-lg text-white/90 hover:text-white">
